ikitable\" style=\"font-size: 95%;\"\n|-\n! rowspan=\"2\"|Year\n! rowspan=\"2\"|Date\n! rowspan=\"2\"|{{Tooltip|No.|Car number}}\n! rowspan=\"2\"|Driver\n! rowspan=\"2\"|Team\n! rowspan=\"2\"|Manufacturer\n! colspan=\"2\"|Race Distance\n! rowspan=\"2\"|Race Time\n! rowspan=\"2\"|Average Speed<br />(mph)\n! rowspan=\"2\"|Report\n|-\n! Laps\n! Miles (km)\n|-\n| 1996\n| May 22\n|align=\"center\"|16\n| [[Tim Steele (racing driver)|Tim Steele]]\n| Steele Racing\n| [[Ford]]\n|align=\"center\"|166\n|align=\"center\"|249 (400.727)\n|align=\"center\"|1:48:20\n|align=\"center\"|138.730\n| [https://www.racing-reference.info/race/1996_ADG_EasyCare_400k/A Report]\n|-\n| 1997\n| May 21\n|align=\"center\"|74\n| [[Gary Laton]]\n| Thomas Laton\n| [[Chevrolet]]\n|align=\"center\"|134\n|align=\"center\"|201 (323.478)\n|align=\"center\"|1:58:47\n|align=\"center\"|101.529\n| [https://www.racing-reference.info/race/1997_EasyCare_Certified_200_(May)/A Report]\n|-\n|}\n\n====Manufacturer wins====\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"font-size: 95%;\"\n|-\n! # Wins\n! Manufacturer\n! Years Won\n|-\n! rowspan=2|1\n| [[Ford]]\n| 1996\n|-\n| [[Chevrolet]]\n| 1997\n|}\n{{-}}\n==Former fall race==\n\n{{Infobox motor race\n|Race title = EasyCare Vehicle Service Contracts 150\n|Logo = \n|Track map = Lowe's Motor Speedway.svg\n|Series long = [[ARCA Menards Series]]\n|Series short = AMS\n|Venue = [[Charlotte Motor Speedway]]\n|Location = [[Concord, North Carolina]]\n|Sponsor = [https://easycare.com/ EasyCare]\n|First race = 1996\n|Last race = 2003\n|Distance = {{convert|150|mi|km|abbr=on}}\n|Laps = 100\n|Duration = \n|Previous names = '''First Plus 200''' (1996)<br>'''EasyCare Certified 200''' (1997)<br>'''EasyCare Certified 150''' (1998)<br>'''EasyCare Certified 100''' (1999)<br>'''EasyCare Vehicle Service Contracts 100''' (2000-2002)\n|Most wins driver = [[Tim Steele (racing driver)|Tim Steele]] (2)<br>[[Kirk Shelmerdine]] (2)\n|Most wins team = Steele Racing (2)\n|Most wins manufacturer = [[Ford]] (4)\n|Length mi = 1.5\n|Turns = 4\n}}\n\nThe '''EasyCare Vehicle Service Contracts 150''' was an [[ARCA Menards Series]] race run between 1996 and 2003 during the fall sometime around October 1. The race was removed for the 2004 season. [[Tim Steele (racing driver)|Tim Steele]] and [[Kirk Shelmerdine]] tie for the most wins at two apiece. In the 2001 event, driver [[Blaise Alexander]] was killed in a fatal crash on lap 63.\n\n===Past winnners===\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"font-size: 95%;\"\n|-\n! rowspan=\"2\"|Year\n! rowspan=\"2\"|Date\n! rowspan=\"2\"|{{Tooltip|No.|Car number}}\n! rowspan=\"2\"|Driver\n! rowspan=\"2\"|Team\n! rowspan=\"2\"|Manufacturer\n! colspan=\"2\"|Race Distance\n! rowspan=\"2\"|Race Time\n! rowspan=\"2\"|Average Speed<br />(mph)\n! rowspan=\"2\"|Report\n|-\n! Laps\n! Miles (km)\n|-\n| 1996\n| October 2\n|align=\"center\"|16\n| [[Tim Steele (racing driver)|Tim Steele]]\n| Steele Racing\n| [[Ford]]\n|align=\"center\"|134\n|align=\"center\"|201 (323.478)\n|align=\"center\"|2:06:57\n|align=\"center\"|94.998\n| [https://www.racing-reference.info/race/1996_First_Plus_200/A Report]\n|-\n| 1997\n| October 1\n|align=\"center\"|16\n| [[Tim Steele (racing driver)|Tim Steele]]\n| Steele Racing\n| [[Ford]]\n|align=\"center\"|134\n|align=\"center\"|201 (323.478)\n|align=\"center\"|1:51:06\n|align=\"center\"|108.551\n| [https://www.racing-reference.info/race/1997_EasyCare_Certified_200_(October)/A Report]\n|-\n| 1998\n| September 30\n|align=\"center\"|45\n| [[Adam Petty]]\n| [[Petty Enterprises]]\n| [[Pontiac]]\n|align=\"center\"|67\n|align=\"center\"|100.5 (161.739)\n|align=\"center\"|0:52:12\n|align=\"center\"|115.517\n| [https://www.racing-reference.info/race/1998_EasyCare_Certified_100/A Report]\n|-\n| 1999\n| October 6\n|align=\"center\"|3\n| [[Kirk Shelmerdine]]\n| Kenneth Appling Racing\n| [[Chevrolet]]\n|align=\"center\"|67\n|align=\"center\"|100.5 (161.739)\n|align=\"center\"|0:56:02\n|align=\"center\"|107.678\n| [https://www.racing-reference.inf